# 🤖 AI Agent to Test Websites Automatically Using Natural Language

An intelligent AI-powered end-to-end (E2E) web testing agent that accepts **natural language test instructions**, interprets them using **LangGraph**, auto-generates **Playwright test scripts**, executes them in a headless browser, and produces **detailed test reports** — no manual test code required.

---

## 🎯 Objective

To implement an intelligent agent capable of performing automated end-to-end testing on web applications by bridging the gap between human-readable instructions and executable browser automation scripts.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 📝 **Natural Language Input** — Write test cases in plain English
- 🧠 **LangGraph Agent Orchestration** — Manages the full test workflow pipeline
- ⚙️ **Auto Playwright Script Generation** — Converts instructions to executable scripts
- ✅ **Dynamic Assertion Generation** — Automatically validates expected outcomes
- 🌐 **Headless Browser Execution** — Runs tests without opening a visible browser
- 🔄 **Adaptive DOM Mapping** — Adjusts dynamically to web structure changes
- 📊 **Detailed Test Reports** — Pass/fail summaries with execution details
- 🖥️ **Flask Web Interface** — Clean UI to input tests and view results

---

## 🔄 System Architecture & Workflow

```
start
  ↓
convert_user_instruction_to_actions
  ↓
get_initial_action
  ↓
get_website_state
  ↓
generate_code_for_action  ←─────────┐
  ↓                                  │
validate_generated_action ───────────┘ (retry loop)
  ↓                    ↓
post_process_script   handle_generation_error
  ↓                         ↓
execute_test_case           end
  ↓
generate_test_report
  ↓
end
```

---

## 🧩 Modules

| Module | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| **Instruction Parser** | Interprets natural language test descriptions and maps them to browser actions |
| **Code Generation** | Converts parsed actions into executable Playwright Python scripts |
| **Execution** | Runs tests headlessly and captures runtime logs |
| **Assertion & Reporting** | Validates expected results and compiles human-readable test summaries |

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Component | Technology |
|-----------|-----------|
| Language | Python 3.x |
| Agent Framework | LangGraph |
| Browser Automation | Playwright (Python) |
| Web Framework | Flask |
| LLM Toolkit | LangChain Community (PlaywrightBrowserToolkit) |
| UI (optional) | Streamlit / Gradio |
| Frontend | HTML, CSS, JavaScript |

